<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/main.css">
    <title>About</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/images/small-logo.svg">
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        main {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .centered-section {
            margin: 70px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("Navigation.ejs") %>
    <%- include("Login.ejs") %>
    <%- include("Signup.ejs") %>
    <main>
        <section class="py-5 centered-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-5">
                        <span class="text-muted">My Story</span>
                        <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold">About Me</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-1">
                        <p class="lead">Welcome to WriteWave, a space where I share my journey in backend development. This project is a personal endeavor that I started to sharpen my skills while pursuing my undergraduate degree in computer science.</p>
                        <p class="lead">While I don't have a specific plan for posting regular content here, this platform serves as a way for me to showcase my work and document the technical challenges I’ve overcome. It’s a blog in the sense that it demonstrates my capabilities and progress in web development, rather than being a fully-fledged content site.</p>
                        <p class="lead">This project is all about learning, experimenting, and sharing what I’ve built. I hope that others can find value in seeing how I’ve tackled various development tasks, and perhaps even learn something along the way.</p>
                        <p class="lead">Thank you for visiting and taking an interest in my work.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include("Footer.ejs") %>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>    
    <%- include("navigation_script.ejs") %>
</body>
</html>
